<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> [ADD DATE HERE]</p>

<p>
This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, stored, and protected
when using our Facebook-connected automation application.
</p>

<p>
This application is used to automate Facebook Messenger conversations for a connected
Facebook Business Page.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>a. Facebook Account and Page Information</h3>
<p>
When you connect your Facebook account or Facebook Page, we may collect the following
information provided by Facebook:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Public profile information (name, profile picture)</li>
    <li>Facebook Page name and Page ID</li>
    <li>Messenger messages sent to the connected Facebook Page</li>
    <li>Message timestamps and sender IDs</li>
    <li>Page access tokens required for automation</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>We do NOT collect:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Facebook passwords</li>
    <li>Private messages outside your connected Page</li>
    <li>Payment or financial information</li>
    <li>Personal data unrelated to automation</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>

<p>
Collected data is used strictly for the following purposes:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Automating Facebook Messenger responses</li>
    <li>Executing automation workflows</li>
    <li>Sending and receiving messages on behalf of your Facebook Page</li>
    <li>Maintaining app functionality and reliability</li>
    <li>Preventing abuse and unauthorized access</li>
</ul>

<p>
We do not use collected data for advertising, profiling, resale, or marketing purposes.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>3. Data Storage and Retention</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Message data is processed in real time for automation purposes</li>
    <li>Messages are not permanently stored unless required for workflow logs</li>
    <li>Logs are retained only as long as necessary for operational purposes</li>
    <li>Access tokens are encrypted and stored securely</li>
</ul>

<p>
All data is deleted when:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>The Facebook Page disconnects the app</li>
    <li>The automation workflow is removed</li>
    <li>A valid data deletion request is received</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>

<p>
We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties.
</p>

<p>
Data is shared only:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>With Facebook APIs as required to provide Messenger functionality</li>
    <li>When required by law or valid legal requests</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>5. Facebook Platform Compliance</h2>

<p>
This application complies with Facebook Platform Terms, Facebook Developer Policies,
and Facebook Messenger Platform Policies.
</p>

<p>
Only permissions strictly required for Messenger automation are requested and used.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>6. User Rights and Control</h2>

<p>
You have the right to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Disconnect your Facebook Page at any time</li>
    <li>Revoke app permissions via Facebook account settings</li>
    <li>Request access to or deletion of your data</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>7. Data Deletion Instructions</h2>

<p>
This section serves as the official <strong>Data Deletion Instructions URL</strong>
for Facebook.
</p>

<h3>How to Request Data Deletion</h3>

<p><strong>Option 1: Email Request</strong></p>
<p>
Send an email to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> [YOUR EMAIL ADDRESS]</li>
    <li><strong>Subject:</strong> Facebook App Data Deletion Request</li>
</ul>

<p>
Please include:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Your Facebook Page name</li>
    <li>Your Facebook User ID (if available)</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Option 2: Remove the App</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Go to Facebook Settings → Apps and Websites</li>
    <li>Remove this application</li>
    <li>All associated data will be deleted automatically</li>
</ul>

<p>
All deletion requests are processed within <strong>7 business days</strong>.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>8. Security Measures</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Encrypted access tokens</li>
    <li>Restricted system access</li>
    <li>Limited permission scopes</li>
    <li>Secure automation workflows</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>9. Children’s Privacy</h2>

<p>
This application is not intended for children under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect data from children.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>

<p>
We may update this Privacy Policy as required by law or Facebook policies.
Updates will be reflected by the “Last Updated” date at the top of this page.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>11. Contact Information</h2>

<p>
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or data handling practices,
please contact:
</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Business Name:</strong> [YOUR BUSINESS NAME]</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> [YOUR EMAIL ADDRESS]</li>
    <li><strong>Website:</strong> [YOUR WEBSITE URL]</li>
</ul>

